list of the book I read at the end if you want to dig deeper in the
world of beating the blackjack game. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://brainsorting.com/posts/blackjack-the-21-game/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (22 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>blackjack</category><category>books</category><category>mathematic</category><guid>https://brainsorting.com/posts/blackjack-the-21-game/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2020 20:20:03 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>